		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Slayers are perhaps the most feared of barbarians. Channeling the power of death, a slayer's power lies in murder: both in dealing death and in walking the thin line between life and death. A slayer might be possessed by spirits, calling on necromantic magic, or wielding ancient powers of death and murder.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Slayer</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.camZFNOflfJrHXrF]{Death Haze}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.cPayfG1ZskRXod73]{Life Tap}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.9vv6bcyW2jc0wDBj]{Slay}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.7NrOEx1GXG74mFZj]{Death Curse}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.th1ScN0faFcaJPYM]{Rampage}</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
